            "text_VPmpwM": {
              "type": "text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>StencilFast’s metal stencils are crafted from .080-thick aluminum, making them exceptionally durable and ideal for high-traffic, professional applications. Each aluminum stencil can be cut to fit your project needs, with sizes ranging from 3 inches up to 144 inches. Rolled edges are available upon request.<br/><br/><br/>We specialize in DOT/MUTCD and FAA stencils. Our aluminum stencils are perfectly suited for thermoplastic applications and provide clean, precise markings every time.<br/><br/><br/>For those who need a robust alternative to plastic, aluminum offers the strength and longevity that stand up to the job. Any of our stencils can be produced in aluminum as well as our proprietary 1/10\" orthopedic grade low-density polyethylene plastic.</p>",
